            <summary>Manuscript used in private or public recitation and ceremony in celebration and veneration of the planet Mars (Bhauma), through which the devotee receives benefits, such as the removal of disease, and the obtainment of benefits and gifts, such as the removal of debt (ṛṇa). Manuscript missing one folio (f. 3).</summary>
            <textLang mainLang="san">In Sanskrit</textLang>
